pip install pytest
sudo apt-get upgrade

<1>To test all 
python -m pytest
pytest -v

<2>
py.test
py.test -v


<3>To see the reason why a test is skipped. This is for the test that is marked to skip like: @pytest.mark.skip(reason="I dont want to run this test now")
pytest -v -rxs


<4>This will run a test that has multiply as part of this name
pytest -k multiply
pytest -k multiply -v

<5>
This command will run test that is tagged with windows
pytest -m windows 
pytest -m "not windows"

This command will run test that is tagged with mac
pytest -m mac 


